    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>- Update to version 6.3.2 (swift-6.3.2-RELEASE):
  * Linux worker-thread names and basic thread prioritisation
  * 16 KB page alignment on 64-bit Android
  * Static library build support
  * Build-system updates (CMake bump, FreeBSD/OpenBSD fixes)
- Drop silence-signedness-...-error.patch (merged upstream PR #880)
- Rebase soversion.patch for restructured CMakeLists</comment>
